---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';

const lastUpdated = 'December 24, 2025';
---

<Layout
  title="Privacy Policy - SnapFuel"
  description="Privacy Policy for SnapFuel - Learn how we collect, use, and protect your personal information."
>
  <Header />

  <main class="py-16 bg-white">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 max-w-4xl">
      <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">SnapFuel Privacy Policy</h1>
      <p class="text-gray-600 mb-8">Effective Date: {lastUpdated}</p>

      <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none">
        <section class="mb-8">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">1. Introduction</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
            SnapFuel ("we," "us," or "our") respects your privacy. This Privacy Policy describes how we collect, use, and share your personal data when you use the SnapFuel mobile application (the "Service"). By using the Service, you agree to the collection and use of information in accordance with this policy.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section class="mb-8">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">2. Data We Collect</h2>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-6 text-gray-700 space-y-3 mb-4">
            <li><strong>Personal Identification:</strong> Name, email address (for account creation).</li>
            <li><strong>Physical & Health Data:</strong> Weight, height, age, gender, activity level, calorie intake, water consumption, and dietary preferences (e.g., Vegan, Keto).</li>
            <li><strong>User Content:</strong> Recipes you add manually, notes you take ("Note Raking"), and meal plans you create.</li>
            <li><strong>Multimedia Data (AI Features):</strong>
              <ul class="list-disc pl-6 mt-2 space-y-1">
                <li><strong>Photos:</strong> Images of your fridge, food products, or meals uploaded for AI analysis.</li>
                <li><strong>Barcodes:</strong> Data scanned via camera to retrieve nutritional information.</li>
              </ul>
            </li>
            <li><strong>Device & Usage Data:</strong> IP address, device model, OS version, and app usage logs (via analytics tools like Google Analytics/Firebase).</li>
          </ul>
        </section>

        <section class="mb-8">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">3. How We Use Your Data (Including AI Processing)</h2>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-6 text-gray-700 space-y-3 mb-4">
            <li><strong>To Provide Features:</strong> We process your weight and diet data to calculate daily calorie needs and water intake.</li>
            <li><strong>AI Analysis (Google Gemini):</strong>
              <p class="mt-2 mb-2">When you take a photo of your fridge or a product, that image is transmitted to our AI partner (Google Gemini) to identify ingredients and suggest recipes.</p>
              <p class="mb-2"><strong>Note:</strong> We do not use your private health data to train public AI models, but your inputs are processed by the AI provider to generate responses.</p>
            </li>
            <li><strong>Scanning Services:</strong> Barcode data is sent to nutrition databases to retrieve product facts.</li>
            <li><strong>Monetization:</strong> To manage your Premium subscription status via Apple/Google stores.</li>
          </ul>
        </section>

        <section class="mb-8">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">4. Data Sharing and Third Parties</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
            We do not sell your personal data. We share data only with necessary service providers:
          </p>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-6 text-gray-700 space-y-2 mb-4">
            <li><strong>AI Service Provider:</strong> Google (Gemini API) – for image recognition and text generation.</li>
            <li><strong>Cloud Storage:</strong> (e.g., AWS, Firebase) – to store your user profile and notes securely.</li>
            <li><strong>Analytics:</strong> Google Analytics / Firebase – to understand how the app is used.</li>
            <li><strong>Payment Processors:</strong> Apple App Store and Google Play Store handle all financial transactions. SnapFuel does not see or store your credit card details.</li>
          </ul>
        </section>

        <section class="mb-8">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">5. International Data Transfers</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
            SnapFuel operates globally. Your information, including Personal Data, may be transferred to—and maintained on—computers located outside of your state, province, country, or other governmental jurisdiction where the data protection laws may differ (e.g., servers in the USA). By using SnapFuel, you consent to this transfer.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section class="mb-8">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">6. Your Rights (GDPR & CCPA)</h2>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-6 text-gray-700 space-y-3 mb-4">
            <li><strong>For Users in Europe (GDPR):</strong> You have the right to access, rectify, download, or erase your data. You also have the right to restrict processing. To exercise these rights, contact us at <a href="mailto:futurappsmobile@gmail.com" class="text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-700 underline">futurappsmobile@gmail.com</a>.</li>
            <li><strong>For Users in California (CCPA):</strong> You have the right to know what personal information is collected and to request deletion of your data.</li>
            <li><strong>Account Deletion:</strong> You can request the deletion of your account and all associated data directly within the App settings.</li>
          </ul>
        </section>

        <section class="mb-8">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">7. Data Retention</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
            We retain your personal data only as long as is necessary for the purposes set out in this Privacy Policy or as required by law.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section class="mb-8">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">8. Children's Privacy</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
            SnapFuel is not intended for use by children under the age of 13 (or 16 in certain jurisdictions like the EU). We do not knowingly collect data from minors.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section class="mb-8">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">9. Contact Us</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
            For privacy concerns: <a href="mailto:futurappsmobile@gmail.com" class="text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-700 underline">futurappsmobile@gmail.com</a>
          </p>
        </section>
      </div>
    </div>
  </main>

  <Footer />
</Layout>
